{"tid":1107779,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"高雄市民的心痛","createTime":"2019-04-15T13:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T13:20:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f76b39405fa5ea0348ee2de620ce0d5426bfa59","tid":1107779,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190415/20656034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F20656034&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUatT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=c5843c76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F20656034&h=1249e3b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190415/20656034</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高雄市民的心痛 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190415/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190415%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=de76b0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李碧華拍攝<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n六合夜市是高雄知名夜市之一，吃貨的客似雲來，據說從前生意一般，韓國瑜當上市長，拼旅遊拼經濟，人潮死灰復燃。<br />\n<br />\n不少攤檔都張懸了韓禿子的大照片、看板、漫畫像之類，「音容宛在」守護宣傳，還有市民排隊連署拱韓選總統──形勢比人強，不用「拱」不用「King maker」，誰需要幾位夕陽大老「讓」？酸者都在刷存在感而已。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市民死忠，美國的僑胞還亢奮：「超喜歡！見到他就死而無怨了！」──他們十分關心韓的健康，因韓近日訪美參與哈佛大學閉門座談，又有諸多活動應酬，天冷加時差，疲憊不堪，連在波士頓餐券收費高昂（二千美元）的僑社晚宴，也因身體不舒服而早退，翌晨海外僑民早餐會也來不了，說那旅遊巴士司機因改道迷路，在市區白繞了一個半小時，云云。<br />\n<br />\n市民心痛：「市長身體這樣差，又揉眼睛多次，太累了，怎麼選總統？」、「八字不夠重，要小心保重啊！」、「他就是拼訂單拼到病！」&hellip;&hellip;知道我們是來客，問：「香港市長累壞了你們也心痛吧？」──沒這體驗，一來香港市長們不是市民一人一票選的；二來，市長奔波勞累不是為了港人福祉而是為了個人而媚上邀功，誰心痛得起？  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n在粵港澳大灣區生活的意向的主題性住戶調查 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n奇 人 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"01f520b0729ec3e04d65715db16a6436d0eaffca","tid":1107779,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29456443459ab8d483c492b321527fef6dafd6e1","tid":1107779,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}